umbnailWidth>72</ThumbnailWidth><ThumbnailHeight>70</ThumbnailHeight><ThumbnailBytes>1745</ThumbnailBytes><PhotoType>ViewOfAGuestRoom</PhotoType></Photo><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>General</Type><Text>Completely refurbished in 2008, under the concept of "adults only" aged 16 and over.
For anyone wanting to explore the beautiful city of Palma and yet still enjoy a beach holiday, the Marina Luz is the place to choose. Idyllically located in the Bay of Palma, just a few minutes drive from the Airport, this hotel offers the best of both worlds. Being just a short distance from the cosmopolitan city of Palma, with the picturesque beach of Cala Estancia on its doorstep, the panoramic views of the Bay of Palma from the terraces of the pool and poolside bar are breath-taking. The Marina Luz would suit any couple looking for a relaxing stay.
Recently refurbished with the best of facilities, it now fully meets with the chic standard of the most demanding visitors. Full of plants and deckchairs, its terraces are now undoubtedly one of its greatest attractions and include a lagoon swimming pool and two jacuzzis. The terraces provide the perfect place to enjoy a drink, sunbathe and enjoy wonderful views of the Mediterannean at the same time.
